title: Ending Self-Sabotage
itunes:title: Ending Self-Sabotage
description:
How often have you said "I just don't understand why I do that to myself?" or "I just keep eating when I know I shouldn't." You wonder if you are self-sabotaging, and you put yourself down for doing it.
 
In today's podcast we take a close look at self sabotage: what it is, where it comes from, and we judge ourselves because of it. This podcast really explains the concept and gives a four step process to work through it.
 
 
Get the Free Course here:
